== 觀測 ==
一支俄國觀測隊在[[天山山脈|天山山脈]]西部[[阿賴山脈|阿賴山脈]]中的[[蘇柳克塔|蘇柳克塔]]煤礦地區（今屬吉尔吉斯斯坦）觀測了日全食。巧合的是，當時俄國仍使用[[儒略曆|儒略曆]]，因此日全食當天恰好是1月1日[[元旦|新年]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Затмение 1907 года|url=http://mytashkent.uz/2009/09/21/zatmenie-1907-goda/|publisher=Письма о Ташкенте|date=2009-09-21|accessdate=2016-04-23|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027182336/https://mytashkent.uz/2009/09/21/zatmenie-1907-goda/|dead-url=no}}{{ru}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Observing a Solar Eclipse on January 1, 1907 near the Cherniaevo Station in the Tian-Shan Mountains above the Saliuktin Mines. Golodnaia Steppe|url=https://www.wdl.org/en/item/6567/|publisher=[[世界数字图书馆|世界数字图书馆]]|accessdate=2016-04-23|archive-date=2020-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200519145409/https://www.wdl.org/en/item/6567/|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>

